title: WATCH: Father Daughter Duo Sing 'How Far I'll Go' With Auli'i Cravalho From Moana | Letty B | KISS 95.7
text:
share 
Source: EllenTube 
This is too CUTE! Auli'i Cravalho, the voice of Moana, sang with adorable 4 year old Claire and her dad Dave played guitar. They appeared on the Ellen show today (2/27) following her beautiful performance last night at the Oscars!
